4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals seeking to enter the field without prior experience. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 students per class. Participants gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, and network administration, while developing skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Courses are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop